{"id":"guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale","title":"設定執行時語言環境","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <!-- \nPlaceholder page; keep in case 3rd party links to it. \nIts too brief contents were relocated to `i18n-optional-import-global-variants.md` \nNo longer in navigation.\n -->\n<h1 id=\"set-the-runtime-locale\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"nebrkhef8syxjycznapk0pg5\">設定執行時語言環境<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale#set-the-runtime-locale\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8yhtsjixnvgfdjecjl96agcgr\">Angular 的初始安裝中已經包含了美國英語（<code>en-US</code>）的語言環境資料。當你將 <code>--localize</code> 選項與 <a href=\"cli/build\" title=\"ng build | CLI | Angular\"><code>ng build</code></a> 指令一起使用時，<a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 會自動包含語言環境資料並設定 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 值。</p>\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：Thu Aug 31 2023</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - cli\n - cli/build\n - guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale#set-the-runtime-locale\n-->"}